para_trans: On extending the term of the committee by appointing invited members to the Lokmanya Tilak Charitra Sadhana Prakashan Samiti.
Department of Higher and Technical Education
Government Decision HATH: PHOTO 2024 / Q. 22/721067 MASHI-2
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,

Reference: - (1) Government Decision, Department of Higher and Technical Education, No.2020 / (Q. 78/20) / Aastha-2D. 1st August, 2020 (2) Government Decision, Department of Higher and Technical Education, No.2020 / (Q 78/20) / Aastha-2, Dt. January 22, 2021

Reference No. Under section 1, the Lokmanya Tilak Charitra Sadhana Prakashan Samiti was set up, with a term of three years. Invited members have been appointed to the committee under the HR in question. The government was considering extending the term of the committee by appointing new invitees to the committee.

The following dignitaries, who are biographers of Lokmanya Tilak, have been appointed as invited members on the Lokmanya Tilak Charitra Sadhana Prakashan Samiti vide Government Decision dated 22nd January, 2021.
2. Biography of Lokmanya Tilak along with the above mentioned invited members on the said Committee.
The following faculty members are being newly appointed as invited members.
The term of the said Committee shall be till 30th June, 2024.
4. Government Decision No. The composition of the Committee as prescribed under 1B2,
The Terms and Conditions will remain in place.
5. This Government Decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
